{"tid":210784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明朝既火器好先進好發達!","createTime":"2017-04-21T07:53:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T19:24:01.000Z","uid":41375,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c6ab21d279e84a3cf1b01afa5020c135b63e3eea","tid":210784,"uid":41375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T07:53:38.000Z","msg":"搵到講網站係關於明朝既火器 發覺原來明朝科技好先進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://greatmingmilitary.blogspot.hk/?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgreatmingmilitary.blogspot.hk%2F%3Fm%3D1&d=nqzd6QM3TLyrPp4uhCfCnwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=1d952dea\" target=\"_blank\">http://greatmingmilitary.blogspot.hk/?m=1</a><br />\n不過個網全部英文黎 唔識英文但有興趣既話自己google或希望有人幫手譯<br />\n<br />\nEg<br />\n平曠步戰隨地滾<br />\n<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-T0QY0MBPY0U/WGofA7u2DeI/AAAAAAAADO4/lCzgc_jBwDk4s1aiRVcWBKf5HB7CxunTgCLcB/s1600/ping_kuang_bu_zhan_sui_di_gun.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-T0QY0MBPY0U%2FWGofA7u2DeI%2FAAAAAAAADO4%2FlCzgc_jBwDk4s1aiRVcWBKf5HB7CxunTgCLcB%2Fs1600%2Fping_kuang_bu_zhan_sui_di_gun.jpg&h=ddd59e37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPing Kuang Bu Zhan Sui Di Gun is a cylindrical tree trunk full of poisoned blades, hooks and nails. To propel/roll the tree trunk forward, it is mounted with sixty linked black powder rocket propellers, which also double as short range flamethrowers. The tree trunk is also hollowed out and filled with explosives and blinding dust, and will explodes into a shower of flaming wood splinters, smoke and blinding dust after a predetermined time.<br />\n鋼輪發火<br />\n<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-tsR-IY9csBw/WCkh2LYBZzI/AAAAAAAADKI/pA9242AQ9DM6Q7aLYbtNVLb1JDU59x-WwCLcB/s1600/steel_wheel_igniter.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-tsR-IY9csBw%2FWCkh2LYBZzI%2FAAAAAAAADKI%2FpA9242AQ9DM6Q7aLYbtNVLb1JDU59x-WwCLcB%2Fs1600%2Fsteel_wheel_igniter.jpg&h=0aa73aef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nThe workings of Gang Lun Fa Huo<br />\nGang Lun Fa Huo is actually a suprisingly simple device. Save for its friction wheels, entire device can be manufactured relatively easily without specialised skill or equipment. Two pictures below, drawn by myself in Adobe Illustrator, show the workings of a Gang Lun Fa Huo in basic configuration. There are actually several different configurations for this device, although all work on the same principle."},{"pid":"de41bc642fa73a8eadd234924b7d924de4086920","tid":210784,"uid":41375,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:06:21.000Z","msg":"五雷神機<br />\n<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-7x015dTkdJ8/VkkvhFmPacI/AAAAAAAABrI/l4ctI04Z_ug/s1600/wu_lei_shen_ji.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-7x015dTkdJ8%2FVkkvhFmPacI%2FAAAAAAAABrI%2Fl4ctI04Z_ug%2Fs1600%2Fwu_lei_shen_ji.png&h=3f6040e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n奇勝銃<br />\n<img src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-LJyOFdkHkp0/Vladxj2x65I/AAAAAAAAB3I/j9Adiap1smI/s1600/qi_sheng_chong.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-LJyOFdkHkp0%2FVladxj2x65I%2FAAAAAAAAB3I%2Fj9Adiap1smI%2Fs1600%2Fqi_sheng_chong.jpg&h=a0afa4a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"519c096e508bbabd35cf7196d583ab205591cc00","tid":210784,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T09:23:00.000Z","msg":"但打輸後金<br />\n又要同葡萄牙入貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要比海盜打到縮返入老母個西度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明朝火器天下第一"},{"pid":"c6856a98ba082ef2119cf6337a1b9c6d45312514","tid":210784,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T09:24:52.000Z","msg":"希臘火先勁"},{"pid":"8b6e0bca3ad3ad09831b407ceb8035919c16614a","tid":210784,"uid":29188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"