url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2Fe4d00031f9e45805a7f&d=nqzd6QM3TLyrPp4uhCfCnwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=32f01c86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://i1.kknews.cc/large/e4d00031f9e45805a7f</a><br />\n東北の番筒<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/large/e4a0008ab42512d91c5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2Fe4a0008ab42512d91c5&d=nqzd6QM3TLyrPp4uhCfCnwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=b7763e7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://i2.kknews.cc/large/e4a0008ab42512d91c5</a><br />\n肥前の鉄炮</blockquote><br />\n屌你咩呢啲重衰齋貼 content farm link"},{"pid":"fe40e5c48717fda3cf8db69f02d4112c2ebbb1a6","tid":210784,"uid":41375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T18:20:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-LJyOFdkHkp0/Vladxj2x65I/AAAAAAAAB3I/j9Adiap1smI/s1600/qi_sheng_chong.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-LJyOFdkHkp0%2FVladxj2x65I%2FAAAAAAAAB3I%2Fj9Adiap1smI%2Fs1600%2Fqi_sheng_chong.jpg&h=a0afa4a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-JIj5R6YwaaA/Vlad8cDmSeI/AAAAAAAAB3Q/54cvej8nsk4/s1600/yi_hu_chong.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-JIj5R6YwaaA%2FVlad8cDmSeI%2FAAAAAAAAB3Q%2F54cvej8nsk4%2Fs1600%2Fyi_hu_chong.jpg&h=66dfdf92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-4sMQARAelbM/VlaeF5DI8OI/AAAAAAAAB3Y/C2-779t-Eyc/s1600/xuan_ji_yi_hu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-4sMQARAelbM%2FVlaeF5DI8OI%2FAAAAAAAAB3Y%2FC2-779t-Eyc%2Fs1600%2Fxuan_ji_yi_hu.jpg&h=eb3548db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0eb51b5408303ba19b7a9fa94472e125e4cc7893","tid":210784,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T18:44:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但打輸後金<br />\n又要同葡萄牙入貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要比海盜打到縮返入老母個西度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明朝火器天下第一</blockquote><br />\n有槍大撚曬咩！天下無敵？<br />\n有槍一定贏戰爭㗎？<br />\n<br />\nBtw唔係大中華膠，極度崇洋眉外撚"},{"pid":"0a9312c8786d68e8f7001d0fbfaadfaad126ee97","tid":210784,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T19:24:01.000Z","msg":"夫今強敵（蒙古人）之技，遠惟弓矢，近惟腰刀。&hellip;&hellip;弓矢射不能及遠，近可五十步，使我兵敢於趨前擁斗，敵矢不過三發，則短兵相接，弓矢無用矣，此無足畏也。&hellip;&hellip;銃盡發則難以更番，分發則數少而不足以卻聚隊。手槍打造腹口欠圓，鉛子失制，發之百無一中，則火器不足以與彼矢敵矣。<br />\n<br />\n這句話簡單翻譯一下，戚繼光的意思就是明朝的火槍，既鳥銃的質量非常差，不僅數量不足以組編成真正的部隊，而且製作工藝也非常差，這就導致了鳥銃「百發不中」，連蒙古人的弓箭都比不上，更別說拿出來打仗了。所以鳥銃鳥銃，基本也就打打鳥。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/history/z6x8l5l.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fhistory%2Fz6x8l5l.html&d=nqzd6QM3TLyrPp4uhCfCnwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=4fbbfc21\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/history/z6x8l5l.html</a>"}]}